(1742, 'Boxing: Martial artist of Vietnamese origin knockout &amp;quot;Oriental unbeaten&amp;quot; US', 'Boxing:-Martial-artist-of-Vietnamese-origin-knockout-\"Oriental-unbeaten\"-US', '', '1', '<p><br /> 34 original boxer Vietnam pounding blow out \"surrender\" young American star.</p>', '&lt;p&gt;Tuesday night (21/2) at the Premier Boxing Champions event took place in Houston, Texas (USA), Vietnamese American boxers - Dat Nguyen (34) made his 10-year-old boxer poor taste first defeat first in his career. Earlier Miguel Flores (24) played 21 games and won all.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;news-image&quot; src=&quot;http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2017/images/2017-02-22/1487755537-dat3.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Boxing: V&amp;otilde; sĩ gốc Việt đo v&amp;aacute;n &amp;amp;#34;Đ&amp;ocirc;ng phương bất bại&amp;amp;#34; Mỹ - 1&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Dat Nguyen boxer 34, Vietnamese Americans&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;The match scheduled to take place in 10 innings, but the next inning Dat Nguyen has 6 knock-out opponents with fists pounding powerful forehand.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;A victory showed &quot;the older spicy ginger&quot;, experience will sometimes youth prevailed.&amp;nbsp;With this victory Dat Nguyen has increased the number of career wins to 20 (7 knock-out), he also lost just 2 games in mere career.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Dat Nguyen was born on 10/10/1982 know in Bien Hoa Vietnam. At the age of 8 years old, he left Vietnam with her mother settled in Hawaii (USA), grew up on the beautiful island of Maui. At 12 Dat won Olympic boxing youth championship in the United States set a solid foundation for his boxing career later.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Dated 05.01.2004, marked a milestone of Dat when he first entered professional boxing competitions. &quot;Boxing is not the first choice for my mother. But she encouraged me to