(1757, 'Many English teachers quit because entangled regulations', 'Many-English-teachers-quit-because-entangled-regulations', '', '1', '<p>23-2 morning, Secretary of HCM City Party Dinh La Thang had a meeting with the City Department of Education and Training on the issue of self - socialization and development oriented education and training sector HCMC 2020, vision 2030.</p>', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;news-image&quot; src=&quot;http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/1-2017/images/2017-02-24/1487901235-1.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;Nhiều gi&amp;aacute;o vi&amp;ecirc;n tiếng Anh bỏ nghề v&amp;igrave; vướng quy định - 1&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;At the meeting, Secretary Dinh La Thang directing the education sector must promote autonomy and social mobilization to call for investment of the people for the development of education. However, autonomy must have a roadmap, publicity, transparency and consensus of the parents.&amp;nbsp;At the same time Secretary of education required to study the mechanisms and policies to pay for teachers (GV), not leveling, deserve preferential treatment to attract great people. Industry roadmap to reduce the load programs for students (HS) HS right now that too much study and examination. &quot;We must create conditions for students to have fun, entertainment and sports training, not to students becoming&quot; slaves &quot;of the curriculum.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;Industry must also put an end education is more widespread cause negative and contrary provisions between now and 2020. But the weak and the remedial HS HS fostering good is the responsibility of the schools to do &quot;- Secretary ups required.&amp;nbsp;According to the Department of Education and Training, for the current fiscal autonomy schools can not 100% because many provisions that entangled controlled schools.&lt;/p&gt;\n&lt;p&gt;As for personnel, the City has delegated the recruitment, hiring and school self-balancing some positions as supervisors, counselors manning psychol